transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Haan ji madam bol raha hu.
Customer: Hello?
Customer: Hello? Aapki voice break ho rahi hai.
Customer: Haan madam. Madam ye jo thoda sa mera catalog hai thoda sahi karo isme thoda kuch kuch utpatan likhe hue hai. Maine kafi sare photo dale hai aapke wo whatsapp pe.
Customer: To uske hisab se wo best
Customer: To wo photo dekho.
Customer: Haan. To inko dal ke inke hisab se kuch wo changes karane hai mujhe.
Customer: To abhi to mai thoda sa
Customer: Haan us hisab se kya wo naam vagaira kuch utpatan likhe hue hai.
Executive: Ek minute rukiyega.
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Ek minute rukiyega.
Customer: Ek bar maine catalog jo bheja usme wo sab naam likhe hue hai unke. Wo sabke niche naam likha hua hai unka.
Customer: Us hisab se chala ke fir likhwao madam aap.
Executive: Ek minute rukiyega please.
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Naam likhne hai aapko naam change karne hai aapko?
Customer: Haan naam bhi likhne hai wo jaise dalne the wo sare ke sare wo laptop pe dekh raha hu na to PDF sari aake usme khul rahi hai.
Executive: Ek minute rukiyega sir mai aapko dobara se call kar rahi hu aapki voice na kafi jyada break ho rahi hai. Haan madam mai thoda sa abhi kahi bahar aa gaya tha.
Customer: To sir aap free hai?
Customer: Madam sham ko 4:30 baje phone kare karu mai aapko?
Executive: Kab free hai aap?
Customer: Sham ko 4:00 4:30 baje.
Executive: Haan to theek hai. 4:30 baje ek bar call kar leti hu.
Customer: Haan mai 4:00 4:30 baje aapko ek bar ring kar dunga aap uske baad call kar lena. Mai thoda sa bahar nikal gaya tha abhi. Theek hai madam. 
Executive: Theek hai sir abhi aap jab aap notification aayega na jab aap fatafat karna.
